                                                    <a href="../sarova_whitesands">
                                                        <h3>Sarova Whitesands</h3>
                                                    </a>
                                                    <p>This resort boasts an impressive range of high-quality amenities, making it a popular choice for both couples and families. It has received multiple awards and spans across 22 acres of lush beachfront gardens along Bamburi Beach, which is renowned as one of the finest beaches on the north coast of Mombasa.

The resort offers a wide array of facilities catering to all age groups, including five swimming pools, tennis courts, a gym, and volleyball courts. Additionally, there are clubs for both children and teenagers to keep them engaged and entertained.

Located on a beautiful beach, the resort provides an extensive selection of water sports for guests to enjoy. For those seeking relaxation, the Tulia Spa offers delightful treatments.

A diverse range of restaurants caters to various tastes, and several bars serve delicious beverages. Guests can also visit the disco, which hosts regular live entertainment.

The resort is conveniently located approximately 40 minutes away from Mombasa airport.</p>
